'''Michael Paul Levin''' was a voice actor who provided the voice for [[Duno Dree]] in the [[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent (audio drama)|audio drama]] based on the novella [[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent (audio drama)|Dark Forces: Rebel Agent audio drama]], and also voiced characters in the [[Crimson Empire (audio drama)|audio drama version of ''Crimson Empire'']].<ref name="Crimson Empire">[[Crimson Empire (audio drama)|''Crimson Empire'' audio drama]]</ref>

